### Data Backup

```javascript
// Automated backup
const backup = async () => {
  const data = await client.export({
    resources: ['Patient', 'Observation'],
    dateRange: 'last-7-days'
  });
  
  await uploadToCloud(data);
  await verifyBackup(data);
};
```

